snippet.title: Laser Disco Defenders - PS Vita Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Join the Laser Disco Defenders in this brand new shoot em up for the PlayStation Vita coming in summer 2016. Destroy Lord Monotone's minions by shooting lasers that bounce around the map indefinitely. The more lasers you shoot, the more dangerous the battleground!
